entries.title: GOP move to add 'welfare' to subcommittee name sparks Democratic outrage
entries.description: Democrats reacted harshly to the decision of Republicans on the Ways and Means Committee to add the word “welfare” to the name of a subcommittee.

entries.title: SPN: Fewer government regulations could help alleviate housing crisis
entries.description: (The Center Square) – Three out of every four voters agree that housing affordability is a problem, with many saying they would like to see government take more direct action in easing the burden for residents, a new State Policy Network (SPN) poll finds.
